                                           Table "public.reports"
      Column      |            Type             | Collation | Nullable |               Default               
------------------+-----------------------------+-----------+----------+-------------------------------------
 id               | integer                     |           | not null | nextval('reports_id_seq'::regclass)
 reporter_id      | integer                     |           | not null | 
 reported_user_id | integer                     |           | not null | 
 message_id       | integer                     |           |          | 
 group_id         | integer                     |           |          | 
 reason           | text                        |           | not null | 
 status           | character varying(20)       |           |          | 'pending'::character varying
 admin_notes      | text                        |           |          | 
 reviewed_by      | integer                     |           |          | 
 reviewed_at      | timestamp without time zone |           |          | 
 created_at       | timestamp without time zone |           |          | now()
Indexes:
    "reports_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "idx_reports_created_at" btree (created_at)
    "idx_reports_status" btree (status)
Foreign-key constraints:
    "reports_group_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (group_id) REFERENCES community_groups(id)
    "reports_message_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (message_id) REFERENCES group_messages(id)
    "reports_reported_user_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (reported_user_id) REFERENCES users(id)
    "reports_reporter_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (reporter_id) REFERENCES users(id)
    "reports_reviewed_by_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (reviewed_by) REFERENCES users(id)

